reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater stylish, with one noting it looks more expensive than its price, and appreciate its versatility as it can be dressed up or down.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice sweater all around
items.body: This sweater is gorgeous, comfy, soft and can be dressed up or down. The reviews said it was short, however it fit me nicely, just past the waist line. I must be shorter waisted than some. I absolutely do not like a top that is too short revealing skin every time I raise my arms, at the same time I don’t always want a top to go past my rear end! Read more
items.author: Suz

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super soft and pretty!
items.body: This sweater is so soft and comfortable. It is stylish and I always get compliments when I wear it. It is just the right weight and such a good value for the price. It washes well and the color is just as advertised. It is a very good quality sweater and you won't be disappointed! Read more
items.author: AmazonAddict

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Adorable, runs a little big
items.body: Adorable sweater. Runs a little big-I ordered the small based on reviews even thought it recommended a medium and it fits well. A little boxy. I was worried the cropped look in the photos but length was perfect (I'm 5ft, 130). Softer than I thought, definitely not scratchy. Blue was not as vibrant as the photo, but more of a smoky light blue. Still pretty and I will keep it. Read more
items.author: stacia hays

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice quality design sweater
items.body: Love the design, material super soft, fit is perfect for oversized and not too short. Does shed a little but not as much as other scarfs, gloves I have with similar material. Super soft, even after a few washes. Read more
items.author: Jessica Payson

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars It’s OK.
items.body: It’s beautiful and soft. The color is nice and it fits well. Unfortunately it leaves fuzz EVERYWHERE! My pants are covered in fuzz within a shockingly small amount of time. I don’t expect it to last very long. Read more
items.author: Customer

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Adorable sweater for young adult woman
items.body: Pleasantly surprised by the look and feel of this sweater. It is soft and looks much more expensive than it cost. Has an anthropologie look about it. True to size. Has some stretch but not bouncy. Very comfortable. Read more
items.author: Carrie

items.title: 1.0 out of 5 stars Pills terrible
items.body: I really wanted to love this. Fabric felt super soft but it PILLED sooo bad after the first wear. It was also weird that there are no tags. So I don’t know what the fabric content is. It’s really cute but not wearable. Unfortunately I have to return. Read more
items.author: Sew Whit

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value
items.body: This sweater is adorable. I ordered my tts (small) and it fits great. The fabric is a nice quality. The color is so pretty. I’ve worn it multiple times already .. casually w/jeans & dressier with pants for work. Read more
items.author: FN

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Deep Green, Grass Green, Solid Grey, Floral Blue, Light Apricot, Apricot, Pure Pink, Black and White, Black, Dusty Blue, Pure Blue, Pure Black, Pure Deep Blue, Pure Grey. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
